{"tid":1808011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"場運動直接救左香港，因為咁先block哂蝗團湧港，唔係香港可以已經新沙士大爆發了。","createTime":"2020-01-02T06:08:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T14:01:39.000Z","uid":27451,"like":431,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5e21a7888d804bb78d4acae4393931e0a7e24c43","tid":1808011,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:08:36.000Z","msg":"如果唔係因為場運動，蝗團有無可能會停?<br />\n<br />\n不過新年都一定會湧大量蝗黎香港，好新港蝗話香港亂死左返上場，如果佢地佢上面病毒大爆發，班新港蝗又會湧返黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f89b59dad955484af8a655ef230977b0738884d","tid":1808011,"uid":334861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:09:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ca666f6ca657c1985dd5af37aa8376fa08e7aca","tid":1808011,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:12:28.000Z","msg":"好驚上面會新年放哂班蝗團黎香港攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35b1468a2e2759d757bb0085162c694c4ee9347","tid":1808011,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c1343b82e97cadb29676b91f52eda59e0bfb53","tid":1808011,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"咪撚比蝗黎"},{"pid":"6df5a9691c444c9f65f3d4265db42118082b38d3","tid":1808011,"uid":273218,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"3ca666f6ca657c1985dd5af37aa8376fa08e7aca","tid":1808011